MUTANT51
Fault category: Action
Fault: Incorrect action executed
Failure description: Incorrect selection of shapes.
WIMP/post-WIMP: post-WIMP
Ad-hoc widgets involved: yes
interactions: DnD, button click
Test case length: 4 (Import template, Select shape, Add shape, Select Shapes)
Minimal number of events to perform: 5 (press menu, press button, press canvas (Select), move canvas, release canvas)

The mutated file is package  net.sf.latexdraw.instruments.Hand.
The mutated code is the operation updateAction() in the DnD2Select class.

To produce the failure:
1. Draw one or more shapes on canvas
2. Click on select in the tool bar
3. Drag and drop on canvas to select one shape
-> All shapes on canvas drawn are selected.